{
  "info": {
    "name": "KOSMO API v2",
    "description": "KOSMO API v2 — Spec-Driven Development con documentos enriquecidos y URLs amigables.\n\nIDs: ULID con prefijo tipado (prj_, feat_, spec_, usr_, apk_, aud_).\nSlugs: generados automaticamente desde el nombre. Aceptados en todas las rutas con {project_id} o {feature_identifier}.\n\nRutas duales:\n  /api/v1/projects/sistema-gestion-inventario           ← slug\n  /api/v1/projects/prj_01KT...                            ← ID\n  /api/v1/projects/mi-proyecto/features/alertas-stock      ← ambos slugs\n  /api/v1/features/feat_01KT.../status                     ← solo ID (standalone)\n\nDocumentos: arbol JSON tipado (ProseMirror/TipTap) con indice de navegacion.\nErrores: RFC 7807 Problem Detail (Content-Type: application/problem+json).\nFechas: ISO-8601 UTC con sufijo Z. UTF-8 end-to-end.\n\nEjecutar en orden dentro de cada carpeta.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "access_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "refresh_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "email", "value": "demo@kosmo.app", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "password", "value": "Demo1234!Secure", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "project_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "feature_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "spec_id", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST Register",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": ["function s(k,v){pm.collectionVariables.set(k,v);if(pm.environment&&pm.environment.name)pm.environment.set(k,v)}","pm.test('201 o 409',()=>pm.expect([201,409]).to.include(pm.response.code));","if(pm.response.code===201)s('user_id',pm.response.json().id)"], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"email\":\"{{email}}\",\"password\":\"{{password}}\"}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","register"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Authorize (PKCE)",
          "event": [
            { "listen": "prerequest", "script": { "exec": ["function b64(w){return CryptoJS.enc.Base64.stringify(w).replace(/\\+/g,'-').replace(/\\//g,'_').replace(/=+$/,'')}","var v=b64(CryptoJS.lib.WordArray.random(48));","pm.collectionVariables.set('code_verifier',v);","pm.collectionVariables.set('code_challenge',b64(CryptoJS.SHA256(v)))"], "type": "text/javascript" }},
            { "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["function s(k,v){pm.collectionVariables.set(k,v);if(pm.environment&&pm.environment.name)pm.environment.set(k,v)}","pm.test('201',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(201));","s('authorization_code',pm.response.json().authorization_code)"], "type": "text/javascript" }}
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"email\":\"{{email}}\",\"password\":\"{{password}}\",\"code_challenge\":\"{{code_challenge}}\",\"code_challenge_method\":\"S256\",\"scopes\":[\"read\"]}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/authorize", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","authorize"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Token",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": ["function s(k,v){pm.collectionVariables.set(k,v);if(pm.environment&&pm.environment.name)pm.environment.set(k,v)}","pm.test('200',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(200));","var b=pm.response.json();","s('access_token',b.access.token);","s('refresh_token',b.refresh.token)"], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"grant_type\":\"authorization_code\",\"code\":\"{{authorization_code}}\",\"code_verifier\":\"{{code_verifier}}\"}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/token", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","token"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Proyectos",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST Crear Proyecto",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": ["function s(k,v){pm.collectionVariables.set(k,v);if(pm.environment&&pm.environment.name)pm.environment.set(k,v)}","pm.test('201',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(201));","var b=pm.response.json();","s('project_id',b.id);","pm.test('fase=descubrimiento',()=>pm.expect(b.current_phase).to.eql('descubrimiento'));","console.log('Proyecto',b.id,b.name)"], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"name\":\"Sistema de Gestion de Inventario\",\"description\":\"Un sistema que permite a pequenas empresas gestionar su inventario en tiempo real, controlar stock, generar reportes y recibir alertas de bajo inventario.\"}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","projects"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Listar Proyectos",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","projects"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Obtener Proyecto",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","projects","{{project_id}}"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Discovery",
      "description": "Documento enriquecido (JSON tree) con soporte para bold, italic, strike, listas, citas, code blocks y horizontal rules. Incluye indice de navegacion extraido de headings.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST Generar Discovery",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": ["pm.test('200',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(200));","var b=pm.response.json();","console.log('Secciones:',b.sections.length);","b.sections.forEach(s=>console.log('  ['+s.level+']',s.title,'-> #'+s.anchor))"], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/discovery/generate", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","projects","{{project_id}}","discovery","generate"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Discovery",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": ["pm.test('200',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(200));","var b=pm.response.json();","console.log('Nodos:',b.document.content.length,'| Secciones:',b.sections.length)"], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/discovery", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","projects","{{project_id}}","discovery"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "PUT Guardar Discovery",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": ["if(pm.response.code===200){var b=pm.response.json();console.log('Guardado. Secciones:',b.sections.length)}else if(pm.response.code===422)console.log('Invalido:',pm.response.json().detail)"], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"document\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2,\"id\":\"vision\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Visión del producto\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Plataforma \"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"bold\"}],\"text\":\"web\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" de gestión de inventario.\"}]},{\"type\":\"bulletList\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Control de stock\"}]}]},{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Alertas de inventario\"}]}]}]}]}}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/discovery", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","projects","{{project_id}}","discovery"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Regenerar Discovery",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": ["if(pm.response.code===200){var b=pm.response.json();console.log('Regenerado. Secciones:',b.sections.length)}else console.log(pm.response.json().detail)"], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/discovery/regenerate", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","projects","{{project_id}}","discovery","regenerate"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Features",
      "description": "POST /generate auto-persiste 5 features. POST /suggest devuelve 3 alternativas (no persiste). Features solo editables en estado Borrador.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST Generar Features (5, persiste)",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": ["pm.test('200',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(200));","var d=pm.response.json();","pm.test('5 features',()=>pm.expect(d.features.length).to.be.at.least(3));","d.features.forEach((f,i)=>console.log('  '+(i+1)+'.',f.title,'('+f.id+')'));","if(d.features.length>0)pm.collectionVariables.set('feature_id',d.features[0].id)"], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/features/generate", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","projects","{{project_id}}","features","generate"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Sugerir Alternativas (3, NO persiste)",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": ["if(pm.response.code===200){var d=pm.response.json();console.log('Sugerencias:',d.suggestions.length);d.suggestions.forEach((s,i)=>console.log('  '+(i+1)+'.',s.title))}"], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/features/suggest", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","projects","{{project_id}}","features","suggest"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Sugerir desde Idea",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": ["if(pm.response.code===200)console.log('Sugerencia:',pm.response.json().title)"], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"idea\":\"Alertas de stock bajo con notificaciones automaticas por email\"}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/features/suggest-from-idea", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","projects","{{project_id}}","features","suggest-from-idea"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Crear Feature",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": ["pm.test('201',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(201));","var b=pm.response.json();","pm.collectionVariables.set('feature_id',b.id);","console.log('Creada:',b.id,b.title)"], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"title\":\"Gestion de alertas de stock bajo\",\"description\":\"Permite configurar umbrales minimos de stock por producto y recibir notificaciones por email cuando el inventario alcance niveles criticos.\"}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/features", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","projects","{{project_id}}","features"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Listar Features",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/projects/{{project_id}}/features", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","projects","{{project_id}}","features"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "PATCH Toggle Status",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": ["pm.test('200',()=>pm.response.to.have.status(200));","console.log('Status:',pm.response.json().status)"], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/features/{{feature_id}}/status", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","features","{{feature_id}}","status"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Mejorar Feature (IA)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/features/{{feature_id}}/improve", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","features","{{feature_id}}","improve"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Aplicar Mejora",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"title\":\"Gestion avanzada de inventario con alertas inteligentes\",\"description\":\"Sistema de gestion de inventario con alertas predictivas basadas en patrones historicos de consumo.\"}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/features/{{feature_id}}/apply-improvement", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","features","{{feature_id}}","apply-improvement"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "5. Requisitos",
      "description": "Documento enriquecido de requisitos EARS por feature. Feature debe estar Aprobada para generar (409 si Borrador).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET Requisitos",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/features/{{feature_id}}/requirements", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","features","{{feature_id}}","requirements"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Generar Requisitos",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": { "exec": ["if(pm.response.code===200){var b=pm.response.json();console.log('Feature:',b.feature_title,'| Secciones:',b.sections.length)}else if(pm.response.code===409)console.log('La feature debe estar Aprobada')"], "type": "text/javascript" }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/features/{{feature_id}}/requirements/generate", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","features","{{feature_id}}","requirements","generate"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "PUT Guardar Requisitos",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"document\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":2},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Requisitos Ubicuos\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":3},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"R-1\"}]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"bold\"}],\"text\":\"Sistema:\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" El sistema debera permitir gestion completa de inventario.\"}]}]}}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/features/{{feature_id}}/requirements", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","features","{{feature_id}}","requirements"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Regenerar Requisitos",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/features/{{feature_id}}/requirements/regenerate", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","features","{{feature_id}}","requirements","regenerate"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "6. Utilidades",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET Health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/health", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["health"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET OpenAPI JSON",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/openapi.json", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api","v1","openapi.json"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
